Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California Coast!

Name: Griffith Park
Description: A large park with many activities for family outings and is the ideal spot for hiking, with a view over downtown Los Angeles.

Name: Santa Monica Pier
Description: A pier with many activities and concessions nearby while having an amazing view of the ocean right next to it.

Name: Sequoia National Park
Description: A national park well known for its forest of one of a kind giant trees, which can reach heights above 200 feet.

Name: Yosemite National Park
Description: A national park that is known for its valleys, waterfalls, and diverse wildlife that makes it a scenic beauty.

Name: Hearst Castle
Description: A huge castle known for its architectual beauty with many extravagant rooms built throughout the giant structure, along with the diverse wildlife that surrounds the castle.
